               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary>                     <p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Nāṟkaraṇavupatēcam</title>, "Teaching on the four <emph rend="italic">karaṇam</emph>s", appears to be a lesson on the four <emph rend="italic">karaṇam</emph>s, that is, the four organs of perceptions.</p>
                     <p>The text is complete.</p>
